@model GrcMvc.Models.DTOs.AssessmentDto
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.Localization
@inject IHtmlLocalizer<SharedResource> L
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = L["Assessment_Details_Title"].Value;
    Layout = "_Layout";
}

<div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row mb-3">
        <div class="col">
            <h2><i class="bi bi-file-text"></i> @L["Assessment_Details_Title"]</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="col text-end">
            <a asp-action="Edit" asp-route-id="@Model.Id" class="btn btn-primary">
                <i class="bi bi-pencil"></i> @L["Edit"]
            </a>
            <a asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-secondary">
                <i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i> @L["BackToList"]
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    @if (TempData["Success"] != null)
    {
        <div class="alert alert-success alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
            @TempData["Success"]
            <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close"></button>
        </div>
    }

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-header" style="background: var(--bg-tertiary);">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">@L["Assessment_GeneralInfo"]</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="row mb-3">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <label class="fw-bold">@L["Assessment_Name"]</label>
                            <p>@Model.Name</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <label class="fw-bold">@L["Assessment_Number"]</label>
                            <p>@Model.AssessmentNumber</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row mb-3">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <label class="fw-bold">@L["Assessment_Type"]</label>
                            <p>@Model.Type</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <label class="fw-bold">@L["Assessment_Status"]</label>
                            <p>
                                <span class="badge @GetStatusBadgeClass(Model.Status)">
                                    @Model.Status
                                </span>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row mb-3">
                        <div class="col-12">
                            <label class="fw-bold">@L["Assessment_Description"]</label>
                            <p>@Model.Description</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-header" style="background: var(--bg-tertiary);">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">@L["Assessment_ResultsAndFindings"]</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="row mb-3">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <label class="fw-bold">@L["Assessment_ComplianceScore"]</label>
                            <p>
                                @if (Model.ComplianceScore.HasValue)
                                {
                                    <span class="badge @GetScoreBadgeClass(Model.ComplianceScore.Value)">
                                        @Model.ComplianceScore%
                                    </span>
                                }
                                else
                                {
                                    <span class="text-muted">@L["Assessment_NotScored"]</span>
                                }
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <label class="fw-bold">@L["Assessment_ReviewedBy"]</label>
                            <p>@(string.IsNullOrEmpty(Model.ReviewedBy) ? "-" : Model.ReviewedBy)</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="fw-bold">@L["Assessment_Results"]</label>
                        @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(Model.Results))
                        {
                            <div class="p-3 rounded" style="background: var(--bg-tertiary);">@Model.Results</div>
                        }
                        else
                        {
                            <p class="text-muted">@L["Assessment_NoResults"]</p>
                        }
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="fw-bold">@L["Assessment_Findings"]</label>
                        @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(Model.Findings))
                        {
                            <div class="p-3 rounded" style="background: var(--bg-tertiary);">@Model.Findings</div>
                        }
                        else
                        {
                            <p class="text-muted">@L["Assessment_NoFindings"]</p>
                        }
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="fw-bold">@L["Assessment_Recommendations"]</label>
                        @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(Model.Recommendations))
                        {
                            <div class="p-3 rounded" style="background: var(--bg-tertiary);">@Model.Recommendations</div>
                        }
                        else
                        {
                            <p class="text-muted">@L["Assessment_NoRecommendations"]</p>
                        }
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-header" style="background: var(--bg-tertiary);">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">@L["Assessment_ScheduleAndAssignment"]</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="fw-bold">@L["Assessment_StartDate"]</label>
                        <p>@Model.StartDate.ToShortDateString()</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="fw-bold">@L["Assessment_EndDate"]</label>
                        <p>@(Model.EndDate?.ToShortDateString() ?? "-")</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="fw-bold">@L["Assessment_AssignedTo"]</label>
                        <p>@Model.AssignedTo</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-header" style="background: var(--bg-tertiary);">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">@L["Assessment_RelatedItems"]</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="fw-bold">@L["Assessment_RelatedRisk"]</label>
                        <p>
                            @if (Model.RiskId.HasValue)
                            {
                                <a asp-controller="Risk" asp-action="Details" asp-route-id="@Model.RiskId">@L["Assessment_ViewRisk"]</a>
                            }
                            else
                            {
                                <span class="text-muted">@L["Form_None"]</span>
                            }
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="fw-bold">@L["Assessment_RelatedControl"]</label>
                        <p>
                            @if (Model.ControlId.HasValue)
                            {
                                <a asp-controller="Control" asp-action="Details" asp-route-id="@Model.ControlId">@L["Assessment_ViewControl"]</a>
                            }
                            else
                            {
                                <span class="text-muted">@L["Form_None"]</span>
                            }
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

@functions {
    private string GetStatusBadgeClass(string status)
    {
        return status?.ToLower() switch
        {
            "completed" => "bg-success",
            "inprogress" or "in progress" => "bg-primary",
            "planned" => "bg-info",
            "delayed" or "overdue" => "bg-danger",
            "cancelled" => "bg-secondary",
            _ => "bg-secondary"
        };
    }

    private string GetScoreBadgeClass(int score)
    {
        return score switch
        {
            >= 90 => "bg-success",
            >= 70 => "bg-info",
            >= 50 => "bg-warning",
            _ => "bg-danger"
        };
    }
}
